<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center;line-height:20.0pt'><b><span
style='font-size:16.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>中華科技大學職員工工作評量施行細則</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal align=right style='text-align:right;line-height:17.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt'>94</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:標楷體'>年</span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt'>2</span><span
style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:標楷體'>月</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:10.0pt'>15</span><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
標楷體'>日校務會議通過</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:27.0pt;text-indent:-27.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>一、為建立本校職員工公平、公正、公開之工作評量制度，憑以辦理職員工成績考核之作業程序，依據本校職員工成績考核辦法訂定中華科技大學職員工工作評量施行細則（以下簡稱本細則）。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:24.0pt;text-indent:-24.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>二、本校職員工任職至學年度終了時屆滿一學年者，辦理工作評量，任職期間如有因事、因病核定留職停薪或因案停職者，均不予辦理。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:27.0pt;text-indent:-27.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>三、評量項目分為工作、品德及學識等三大項，前開三大項再細分為二十小項（詳見本細則四）。</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>評量方式分為差勤得分和主管評分二部份。職員工自我評量以</span><span lang=EN-US>75</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分為上限，超過上限需提出佐證資料；一級主管根據佐證資料評分，佔個人總分之</span><span
lang=EN-US>63</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>％，副校長評分佔</span><span
lang=EN-US>10</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>％，校長評分佔</span><span
lang=EN-US>20</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>％，差勤分數佔</span><span
lang=EN-US>7</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>％</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>四、評量分項如下</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:12.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>（一）</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>工作（</span><span
lang=EN-US>50</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>分）；包含工作態度、能力及績效，其細項如下：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>主管交付任務之積極性及配合度。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:36.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp;2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>工作效率及效益。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>具創造力能解決問題。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>對於工作能做有效之規劃、執行、追蹤及考核。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>5.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>所完成工作的品質。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>6.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>對於突發事件及危機處理能力。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>7.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>時常對所負責的業務作檢討並改進。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>8.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>可賦予責任而交付工作。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>9.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>有自動自發的工作精神並樂於協助別人。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:45.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>10.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>到勤狀況符合要求。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>（二）品德（</span><span lang=EN-US>25</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分）；其細項如下：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>廉潔自持、公私分明。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>生活嚴謹、無不良嗜好。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>誠實正直、據實以報。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>與人相處融洽親切有禮。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>5.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>富向心力忠誠可靠。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:22.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>（三）學識（</span><span lang=EN-US>25</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>分）；其細項如下：</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>1.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>具豐富之專業知識及分析能力。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>2.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>能適當分辨事務之輕重緩急、把握重點。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>3.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>能接受新觀念及建設性意見。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>4.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>富進取心並參加進修訓練或講習會。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-indent:48.0pt;line-height:22.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US>5.</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>富工作研究潛能具啟發性。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:27.0pt;text-indent:-27.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>五、職員工個人出勤之差勤獎懲紀錄，由人事室列於評量表上，提供職員工個人查對且作為主管評量之依據。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:27.0pt;text-indent:-27.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>六、本校職員工工作自我評量，應於每年六月十日前完成並送交單位一級主管，逾時以六十分計。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:48.0pt;text-indent:-48.0pt;line-height:
22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>七、本校職員工工作評量結果，可作為續聘、調升職、年終績效獎金發放標準等參考資料。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:22.0pt'><span style='font-family:標楷體'>八</span><span
style='font-family:標楷體'>、</span><span style='font-family:標楷體'>本細則經校務會議通過後，陳請校長核定後實施，修正時亦同。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:16.0pt'><span lang=EN-US>&nbsp;</span></p>

